EXTRACTED VALUE: A brave concept fails to disguise a lame racer not worthy of sniffing "F-Zero"'s fumes. [Oct 2007, p.84]
If you love Shrek, and you need your Ogre fix, pick this up as a rental, otherwise I'd skip Shrek the Third the game, and head to the theater instead.
Average, tedious missions and all-round mediocrity make for a pretty dismal night in.
Play basketball on half a court while Chuck D disses your sister. Nope. [June 2008, p.79]
